cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with text-image matching models. It could also belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves text processing. Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories are also possible as they deal with the retrieval of multimedia content based on text queries. Lastly, the Learning (cs.LG) sub-category is also possible as the paper proposes improvements for training and inference of text-image matching models.
